	<contentText >
		<text  position="relative" width="900px" height="auto" left="0" top="0px" ><![CDATA[Jian’s wife recovered quickly and he returned to work. Shortly before the New Year, he met with a supplier whose contract had just been renewed to discuss a new proposal.]]></text>
	</contentText>
